.TH "SVGAELEMENT.SEARCH" "3JS" "October 21, 2025" "JavaScript" "JavaScript Reference Manual"
.SH NAME
SVGAElement.search \- SVGAElement: search property
.SH SYNOPSIS
The \f[B]\f[CB]search\f[B]\f[R] property of the \f[CR]SVGAElement\f[R]
interface returns a string representing the URL\(cqs query string, if
any, including the leading question mark (\f[CR]?\f[R]).
.PP
This property can be set, to change the URL\(cqs query component.
.SH VALUE
A string.
.SH SEE ALSO
.IP \(bu 2
